    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Slide 2 (Problem): Goal=Compare -> Animated visual diagram showing a "GPU Traffic Jam" vs an "FPGA Expressway" -> Justification=Instantly communicates the core latency problem in a universally understood metaphor. -> Method=HTML/CSS/JS.
        - Slide 3 (Solution): Goal=Demonstrate -> Live, interactive HTML mockup of the UI -> Justification=Proves the concept and makes the solution tangible. -> Method=HTML/CSS/JS.
        - Slide 4 (Technology): Goal=Compare -> Multi-metric bar chart -> Justification=Clearly breaks down the multi-faceted technical superiority (cost, power, speed) in a data-driven way. -> Library=Chart.js.
        - Slide 5 (Market): Goal=Organize -> Donut chart for market segmentation -> Justification=Visually shows the targetable market within the larger industry context. -> Library=Chart.js.
        - Slide 7 (Competition): Goal=Organize -> 2x2 Matrix Diagram -> Justification=Classic, powerful tool to strategically position the company. -> Method=HTML/CSS.
        - CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
